resources.string: Students enjoy all-you-care-to-eat dining in a contemporary setting. This exciting location offers fresh made menu items, cutting-edge American entrees, ethnically-inspired foods, vegetarian selections and lots more…\n\nThe Commons also features upscale Premium entrees and fresh baked goods from our in house bakery or local vendors.
The Camden Dining Hall, the Gateway Cafe, is located at the Camden Campus Center.\n\nIt offers a variety of eateries in one convenient location.
